stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PowerOff

    PowerOff --> Startup: power switch on

    Startup --> Initialising: begin setup

    Initialising --> Ready: camera and SD card ready
    Initialising --> Error: initialisation failed

    Ready --> Capturing: shutter button pressed
    Ready --> GalleryMode: gallery mode selected
    Ready --> SettingsMode: mode button pressed
    Ready --> LowBattery: battery below threshold
    Ready --> PowerOff: power switch off

    Capturing --> Saving: image captured successfully
    Capturing --> Error: camera capture failed

    Saving --> PhotoSaved: JPEG written to microSD
    Saving --> Error: SD write failed

    PhotoSaved --> Ready: confirmation complete

    SettingsMode --> SelfTimer: self timer selected
    SettingsMode --> Ready: exit settings

    SelfTimer --> Countdown: shutter button pressed
    Countdown --> Capturing: countdown finished
    Countdown --> Ready: countdown cancelled

    GalleryMode --> Ready: gallery mode closed
    GalleryMode --> Error: Wi-Fi or server error

    LowBattery --> Ready: power restored
    LowBattery --> PowerOff: battery critically low

    Error --> Initialising: retry selected
    Error --> Ready: recoverable error cleared
    Error --> PowerOff: unrecoverable error